rs on the devices.","pos":[91718,91779]},{"content":"Finally, you verified that the devices are properly configured and ready for use.","pos":[91780,91861]},{"content":"Maintain Windows devices and Office 365","pos":[91866,91905]},{"content":"After the initial deployment, you will need to perform certain tasks to maintain the Windows 10 devices and your Office 365 Education subscription.","pos":[91907,92054]},{"content":"You should perform these tasks on the following schedule:","pos":[92055,92112]},{"content":"Monthly.","pos":[92118,92126]},{"content":"These tasks help ensure that the devices are current with software updates and properly protected against viruses and malware.","pos":[92129,92255]},{"content":"New semester or academic year.","pos":[92260,92290]},{"content":"Perform these tasks prior to the start of a new curriculum—for example, at the start of a new academic year or semester.","pos":[92293,92413]},{"content":"These tasks help ensure that the classroom environments are ready for the next group of students.","pos":[92414,92511]},{"content":"As required (ad hoc).","pos":[92516,92537]},{"content":"Perform these tasks as necessary in a classroom.","pos":[92540,92588]},{"content":"For example, a new version of an app may be available, or a student may inadvertently corrupt a device so that you must restore it to the default configuration.","pos":[92589,92749]},{"content":"Table 13 lists the school and individual classroom maintenance tasks, the resources for performing the tasks, and the schedule (or frequency) on which you should perform the tasks.","pos":[92751,92931]},{"content":"Table 13.","pos":[92934,92943]},{"content":"School and individual classroom maintenance tasks, with resources and the schedule for performing them","pos":[92944,93046]},{"content":"Task and resources","pos":[93204,93222]},{"content":"Monthly","pos":[93245,93252]},{"content":"New semester or academic year","pos":[93275,93304]},{"content":"As required","pos":[93327,93338]},{"co